00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:43,980
Palingan kau masuk neraka.

258
00:18:45,740 --> 00:18:48,460
Aku enggak pernah
melakukan perbuatan jahat, loh.

259
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:50,310
Hah?

260
00:18:50,510 --> 00:18:53,160
Kayaknya mereka berniat melawan kita, tuh.

261
00:18:53,260 --> 00:18:54,980
Bikin dongkol.

262
00:18:56,420 --> 00:18:59,250
Luka tusuk di tanganku ini
sudah tidak terasa sakit.

263
00:18:59,260 --> 00:19:02,080
Tangan kananku pun sudah
tak sanggup kuangkat.

264
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,430
Ups.

265
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:15,010
Kayaknya kau bakalan tepar hanya
dengan sejentik jari, Takemicchi.

266
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:18,430
Bang Draken juga.

267
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:24,510
Libas mereka!

268
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:28,240
Ayo, gas! Gas!

269
00:19:25,970 --> 00:19:28,840
Ujung-ujungnya, masa depan tak bisa kuubah.

270
00:19:28,930 --> 00:19:30,820
Maju sini!

271
00:19:30,820 --> 00:19:33,520
Tapi, aku telah berusaha
sekuat tenagaku.

272
00:19:34,020 --> 00:19:37,210
Aku tidak akan menyerah hingga akhir!

273
00:19:40,070 --> 00:19:41,640
Rasakan!

274
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:46,510
Hah?

275
00:19:50,730 --> 00:19:53,060
Kenapa kau terisak begitu?

276
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:57,080
Wahai pahlawan cengeng.

277
00:20:00,410 --> 00:20:01,330
Akkun!

278
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:05,220
Teman-teman.

279
00:20:05,510 --> 00:20:07,680
Kuintet SMP Mizo, tiba!

280
00:20:07,830 --> 00:20:10,070
Wataaaw!

281
00:20:10,610 --> 00:20:11,390
Hah?

282
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:12,970
Hah?!

283
00:20:13,190 --> 00:20:15,130
Tachibana yang mengabari kami!

284
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:17,520
Serahkan pada kami!

285
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:20,680
Kami juga pasti bisa
kalau sudah saatnya!

286
00:20:20,730 --> 00:20:22,260
Berdansa bagai bangau!

287
00:20:22,290 --> 00:20:24,560
Menyengat bagai langau!

288
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:33,540
Dasar tolol!

289
00:20:33,660 --> 00:20:36,060
Cuma karena sampah seperti
kalian berkumpul,

290
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:39,300
kalian pikir bisa melakukan sesuatu?

291
00:20:45,860 --> 00:20:47,410
Bang Draken.

292
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:49,320
Mohon maaf.

293
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:50,710
Hah?

294
00:20:51,870 --> 00:20:53,220
Kalau sendirian ...

295
00:20:54,120 --> 00:20:56,210
... aku pasti takkan bisa melindungimu.

296
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:01,750
Sejak pertama aku kemari,
hingga saat ini,

297
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:04,030
semuanya tak berjalan lancar.

298
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:06,430
Tapi ....

299
00:21:06,850 --> 00:21:09,330
Jangan melakukan hal yang sia-sia.

300
00:21:11,810 --> 00:21:12,250
Oi!

301
00:21:13,610 --> 00:21:14,970
Hal sia-sia?

302
00:21:16,660 --> 00:21:17,740
Sekalipun ...

303
00:21:18,470 --> 00:21:20,270
... perbuatan kami sia-sia ....

304
00:21:22,460 --> 00:21:24,340
Ayo gelut satu lawan satu!

305
00:21:25,850 --> 00:21:27,250
Meskipun begitu ...!

306
00:21:27,690 --> 00:21:29,510
Aku takkan mundur!

307
00:21:29,790 --> 00:21:33,080
Ada kalanya kami takkan mundur!

308
00:21:34,330 --> 00:21:36,740
Iya, 'kan, Takemichi?

309
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:38,380
Hah?

310
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:48,570
Aku pasti takkan kalah!

311
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:50,230
Hah?

312
00:22:00,670 --> 00:22:03,360
Terima kasih, teman-teman.

313
00:22:04,860 --> 00:22:06,880
Kitalah ...

314
00:22:08,010 --> 00:22:09,110
... pemenangnya!

315
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:26,880
Dengan berjalan di sisimu yang
agak bau keringat

316
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:29,790
itu sudah cukup bagiku

317
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:35,810
Seraya dihantam oleh hujan tiba-tiba,

318
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:39,320
kita berciuman di tengah dinginnya malam

319
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:49,070
Kala aku berpaling, masihlah ada
diriku yang kerap tertawa

320
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,250
Tolonglah!

321
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:57,220
Hei, ayo menuju masa depan yang
tak mungkin terwujud!

322
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:59,710
Bawalah aku sekarang juga

323
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,720
ke dunia baru

324
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:06,440
olehmu yang kusebut sebagai "pahlawanku"

325
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,450
Harapan yang blak-blakan

326
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,760
melampaui waktu yang terhenti

327
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:15,710
"Tiada lagi yang kubutuhkan selainmu"

328
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:23,590
Aku akan selalu bernapas di sini

329
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:32,100
Hancurkan jarum yang bengkok

330
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,400
dengan suara tegas

331
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,810
lalu empaskan takdir!


